      <title>Footballer gets sent off for passing wind during game. a google translate story.</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/footballer-gets-sent-off-for-passing-wind-during-game-a-google-translate-story/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jun 2016 09:12:43 +0000</pubDate>
       <guid isPermaLink="false">http://schelp.co.uk/?p=2912</guid> 
      <description>&lt;p&gt;So &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/gossip&#34;&gt;the BBC Website has&lt;/a&gt; the following story. &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Screen-Shot-2016-06-23-at-09.09.52.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Screen Shot 2016-06-23 at 09.09.52&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Screen-Shot-2016-06-23-at-09.09.52-300x65.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&amp;ldquo;A Swedish footballer was sent off for passing wind during a match - with the referee dismissing him for &amp;ldquo;deliberate provocation&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;unsportsmanlike behaviour&amp;rdquo;. (Sport Bladet)
I &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.aftonbladet.se/sportbladet/fotboll/sverige/article23039009.ab&#34;&gt;clicked the link to Sport Blade&lt;/a&gt; t - it is a newspaper in Swedish. I so not speak the Swedish so I looked at the picture and decided the referee was correct to send off this player.
&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Screen-Shot-2016-06-23-at-09.10.06.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Screen Shot 2016-06-23 at 09.10.06&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Screen-Shot-2016-06-23-at-09.10.06-300x263.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
I then copied the &lt;a href=&#34;https://translate.google.co.uk/?client=safari&amp;amp;rls=en&amp;amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;amp;gfe_rd=cr&amp;amp;um=1&amp;amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;amp;hl=en&amp;amp;client=tw-ob#auto/en/Adam%20Lindin%20Ljungkvist%20bj%C3%B6d%20p%C3%A5%20matchens%20r%C3%B6kare.%0ADet%20slutade%20med%20r%C3%B6tt%20kort.%0A%E2%80%93%20Jag%20var%20d%C3%A5lig%20i%20magen%20och%20i%20sista%20minuten%20la%20jag%20av%20en%20brakskit.%20D%C3%A5%20kom%20domaren%20och%20gav%20mig%20ett%20gult%20kort%2C%20sen%20ett%20r%C3%B6tt%2C%20s%C3%A4ger%20v%C3%A4nsterbacken.%0ADen%20m%C3%A4rkliga%20utvisningen%20intr%C3%A4ffade%20i%20division%207-matchen%20mellan%20J%C3%A4rna%20SK%3As%20reservlag%20och%20Pershagens%20SK%2C%20vilket%20L%C3%A4nstidningen%20S%C3%B6dert%C3%A4lje%20var%20f%C3%B6rst%20med%20att%20uppm%C3%A4rksamma.%0AI%20slutskedet%20blev%20Pershagens%20SK%3As%20Adam%20Lindin%20Ljungkvist%2C%2025%2C%20utvisad%20efter%20att%20ha%20f%C3%A5tt%20ta%20emot%20sitt%20andra%20gula%20kort.%20Adam%20Lindin%20Ljungkvist%2C%20som%20spelar%20v%C3%A4nsterback%2C%20fick%20se%20det%20r%C3%B6da%20kortet%20p%C3%A5%20grund%20av%20en%20fis.%0A%E2%80%9DDen%20h%C3%B6rdes%20ordentligt%E2%80%9D%0A%E2%80%93%20Det%20var%20en%20m%C3%A4rklig%20utvisning%2C%20jag%20kan%20knappt%20tro%20p%C3%A5%20det%20sj%C3%A4lv.%20Jag%20var%20d%C3%A5lig%20i%20magen%20och%20i%20sista%20minuten%20la%20jag%20av%20en%20brakskit.%20D%C3%A5%20kom%20domaren%20och%20gav%20mig%20ett%20gult%20kort%2C%20sen%20ett%20r%C3%B6tt%20kort.%20Det%20var%20min%20andra%20varning%20och%20jag%20hade%20ingen%20koll%20p%C3%A5%20min%20f%C3%B6rsta%20alls.%20Jag%20hade%20inget%20minne%20alls.%20Sen%20var%20jag%20lite%20sur%20p%C3%A5%20domaren%2C%20jag%20kunde%20inte%20riktigt%20fatta%20vad%20som%20hade%20h%C3%A4nt.%20Alla%20runt%20omkring%20stod%20och%20asgarvade%2C%20s%C3%A4ger%20Lindin%20Ljungkvist.%0A%E2%80%93%20Det%20jag%20kan%20misst%C3%A4nka%20%C3%A4r%20att%20han%20tror%20att%20jag%20gjorde%20det%20mot%20en%20motst%C3%A5ndare.%20Men%20att%20provocera%20n%C3%A5gon%20med%20en%20prutt%20%C3%A4r%20inte%20speciellt%20smart%20eller%20normalt.%20N%C3%A4%2C%20men%20jag%20la%20bara%20av%20en%20brakskit%20och%20s%C3%A5%20fick%20jag%20r%C3%B6tt%20kort.%20Domaren%20sa%20att%20det%20var%20osportsligt%20beteende.%0ADet%20m%C3%A5ste%20ha%20varit%20en%20riktig%20r%C3%B6kare...%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20Haha.%20Ja%2C%20det%20m%C3%A5ste%20det%20ha%20varit.%20Jag%20s%C3%A5g%20att%20de%20hade%20fr%C3%A5gat%20en%20i%20J%C3%A4rnas%20lag%20och%20han%20sa%20att%20den%20h%C3%B6rdes%20ordentligt.%20Ibland%20har%20man%20ju%20inte%20koll%20p%C3%A5%20om%20det%20%C3%A4r%20den%20lilla%20eller%20stora.%20Man%20tror%20att%20den%20lilla%20kommer%20ut%2C%20men%20den%20l%C3%A5ter%20%C3%A4nd%C3%A5.%0ADu%20brakade%20ihop%20med%20domaren%20efter%C3%A5t%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20Nej.%20Jag%20fr%C3%A5gade%20honom%20p%C3%A5%20ett%20d%C3%A5ligt%20s%C3%A4tt%2C%20men%20det%20var%20inga%20fula%20ord.%20Jag%20var%20irriterad%2C%20samtidigt%20som%20jag%20inte%20kunde%20fatta%20att%20jag%20blev%20utvisad.%0AVar%20det%20ett%20fisf%C3%B6rn%C3%A4mt%20domslut%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20Jag%20tycker%20att%20det%20var%20ett%20skitd%C3%A5ligt%20domslut.%20Nu%20skrattar%20jag%20bara%20%C3%A5t%20det.%20Det%20%C3%A4r%20ingen%20annan%20som%20har%20h%C3%B6rt%20talas%20om%20det%20h%C3%A4r%20innan%2C%20jag%20har%20aldrig%20h%C3%B6rt%20om%20n%C3%A5gon%20som%20blivit%20utvisad%20f%C3%B6r%20att%20man%20fiser.%0A%E2%80%9DSa%20n%C3%A5got%20om%20att%20jag%20var%20en%20pruttare%E2%80%9D%0ANej%2C%20precis.%20Men%20vad%20%C3%A4r%20den%20spontana%20magk%C3%A4nslan%20i%20det%20l%C3%A4get%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20Min%20spontana%20k%C3%A4nsla%3A%20%E2%80%9Dva%2C%20skojar%20du%20med%20mig%3F%E2%80%9D.%20Sedan%20ifr%C3%A5gasatte%20jag%20honom%20innan%20jag%20gick%20d%C3%A4rifr%C3%A5n.%0ANi%20rensade%20luften%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20Han%20sa%20n%C3%A5got%20om%20att%20jag%20var%20en%20pruttare.%20Det%20var%20n%C3%A5got%20s%C3%A5dant.%20Det%20var%20inte%20att%20jag%20stod%20kvar%20i%20flera%20minuter.%20Jag%20sa%20att%20han%20var%20en%20%22pajas%22%20och%20sedan%20gick%20jag%20av%20planen...%0A...det%20var%20bara%20att%20sl%C3%A4ppa%20det.%0A%E2%80%93%20Exakt.%20Ja%2C%20det%20var%20det%20sista%20som%20h%C3%A4nde.%20Det%20var%20i%2093%3Ae%20minuten.%0AHar%20du%20f%C3%A5tt%20n%C3%A5gon%20skit%20f%C3%B6r%20det%20h%C3%A4r%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20F%C3%B6r%20fisen%3F%20Nej%2C%20haha.%20Folk%20har%20bara%20skrattat%20%C3%A5t%20det.%20Inget%20negativt.%20Jag%20bryr%20mig%20inte%20s%C3%A5%20mycket%20heller.%20Det%20%C3%A4r%20naturligt%20att%20l%C3%A4gga%20en%20brakskit%20d%C3%A5%20och%20d%C3%A5.%0AHur%20ser%20du%20p%C3%A5%20resten%20av%20s%C3%A4songen%20f%C3%B6r%20egen%20del%20%E2%80%93%20%C3%A4r%20det%20bara%20att%20gasa%20p%C3%A5%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20Ja%2C%20haha.%20Bara%20att%20k%C3%B6ra%20p%C3%A5.%20Vi%20f%C3%B6rlorade%20med%202-5.%20Men%20det%20kommer%20nog%20g%C3%A5%20b%C3%A4ttre%20resten%20av%20s%C3%A4songen.%0ADu%20%C3%A4r%20en%20spelare%20med%20mycket%20fart%20och%20fl%C3%A4kt...%3F%0A%E2%80%93%20Ja%2C%20det%20%C3%A4r%20jag.%0AMen%20det%20g%C3%A4ller%20att%20h%C3%A5lla%20t%C3%A4tt%20bak%C3%A5t...%0A%E2%80%93%20Ja.%20Och%20dundra%20upp%20bollen%20i%20krysset%20i%20bland%2C%20haha.%0APershagens%20SK%20f%C3%B6rlorade%20matchen%20med%202-5.&#34;&gt;text of the article into google translate&lt;/a&gt;. An internet tool well known for its hermeneutic skills. What proceeded from Google was I believe a word for word translation of the article. (note to self, Swedish newspapers may not prove a long term reading source.)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
